ercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">Revision rounds</div><div class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-semibold\">2 per deliverable</div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/50 backdrop-blur-md p-4\"><div class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">Handoff</div><div class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-semibold\">Source + docs + training</div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 sm:mt-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><h2 class=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 sm:mb-6\">What&#x27;s included</h2><div class=\"grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/40 backdrop-blur-md p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-amber-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\">Brand identity system (logo, typography, color, guidelines)</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/40 backdrop-blur-md p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-amber-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\">Production-ready Next.js website (up to 6 pages)</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/40 backdrop-blur-md p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-amber-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\">AI assistant for lead qualification &amp; FAQs</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/40 backdrop-blur-md p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-amber-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\">Analytics, SEO basics and conversion tracking setup</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/40 backdrop-blur-md p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-amber-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\">90-day growth marketing playbook (SEO + paid + content)</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/40 backdrop-blur-md p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-amber-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\">Copywriting for all primary pages</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/40 backdrop-blur-md p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-amber-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\">2 rounds of revisions per deliverable</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/40 backdrop-blur-md p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-amber-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\">Hand-off documentation &amp; training</span></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 sm:mt-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><h2 class=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 sm:mb-6\">How we engage</h2><ol class=\"relative border-l border-border pl-6 space-y-6\"><li class=\"relative\"><span class=\"absolute -left-[31px] grid h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-brand-pink text-[10px] font-bold text-white\">1</span><div class=\"font-semibold\">Discovery call</div><div class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1 leading-relaxed\">We dig into your goals, constraints, and target market — and tell you honestly if this service is the right fit.</div></li><li class=\"relative\"><span class=\"absolute -left-[31px] grid h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-brand-pink text-[10px] font-bold text-white\">2</span><div class=\"font-semibold\">Proposal &amp; scope</div><div class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1 leading-relaxed\">A fixed-scope proposal with deliverables, timeline, and price. No surprises mid-engagement.</div></li><li class=\"relative\"><span class=\"absolute -left-[31px] grid h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-brand-pink text-[10px] font-bold text-white\">3</span><div class=\"font-semibold\">Build sprints</div><div class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1 leading-relaxed\">Weekly sprints with demos. You see progress every 5 business days and steer direction async.</div></li><li class=\"relative\"><span class=\"absolute -left-[31px] grid h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-brand-pink text-[10px] font-bold text-white\">4</span><div class=\"font-semibold\">Launch &amp; handoff</div><div class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1 leading-relaxed\">We ship to production, set up analytics, and train your team. 30 days of post-launch support included.</div></li></ol></div><section class=\"mt-12 sm:mt-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin h-5 w-5 text-amber-400 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><h2 class=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Business Development Starter Kit<!-- --> — available across 4 regions</h2></div><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4 sm:mb-6 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed\">ClickTake Technologies delivers <!-- -->business development starter kit<!-- --> to clients worldwide from our offices in the UK, Pakistan, USA and Dubai. Local team, local hours, local understanding — global delivery standards.</p><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/40 backdrop-blur-md p-4 hover:border-primary/30 hover:bg-card/60 transition\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-1.5\">🇬🇧</div><div class=\"text-sm font-bold leading-tight\">Birmingham</div><div class=\"text-[11px] text-muted-foreground mb-2\">United Kingdom</div><p class=\"text-[11px] text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-3\">Serving Birmingham, London, Manchester and the Midlands from our registered UK HQ. Available Mon–Sat, 09:30–21:00 GMT.</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] text-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-phone h-3 w-3 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13.832 16.568a1 1 0 0 0 1.213-.303l.355-.465A2 2 0 0 1 17 15h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2A18 18 0 0 1 2 4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-.8 1.6l-.468.351a1 1 0 0 0-.292 1.233 14 14 0 0 0 6.392 6.384\"></path></svg><span class=\"truncate\">+44 7391 653377</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] text-muted-foreground mt-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-3 w-3 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle></svg>GMT</div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/40 backdrop-blur-md p-4 hover:border-primary/30 hover:bg-card/60 transition\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-1.5\">🇵🇰</div><div class=\"text